@OrderService.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5293

### List all orders
GET {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single order by ID (replace with a real ID from the list above)
GET {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Get orders for a customer
GET {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders/customer/CUST-001
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new order
POST {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-042",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "productName": "Widget A",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 49.99,
      "currency": "GBP"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Advance order status: Pending (0) → Confirmed (1) (replace with a real ID)
PATCH {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

###

### Try an invalid transition to see the state machine reject it: Pending (0) → Delivered (3)
PATCH {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 3
}

###

### Health check
GET {{OrderService.API_HostAddress}}/health

###
